title: Trump: 'Nobody talks about' good economic news
description:
(1 Aug 2017) US President Donald Trump complained on Tuesday that the record stock market highs and unemployment lows were not being covered by the news media.
Trump was speaking in the White House's East Room to a gathering of small business owners and entrepreneurs.
"They don't talk about the all time high stock market and they don't talk about another factor, that unemployment just hit a 16 year low," he said.
